Write module test `test/module/file/main.kl` and register in `scripts/run-module-tests.sh` — follow the pattern of existing module tests (7.0–7.2). (per ROADMAP.md section "7.3: File Writing") Tests should cover: write/read-back round-trip, append, overwrite, write_lines with multi-element list and read-back verification.

